
Below are the commands to start server and other ports:

This is to start the HUB

java -jar selenium-server-standalone-2.47.1.jar -role hub 

To View the console below is the command:

http://localhost:4444/grid/console

IE
java -Dwebdriver.ie.driver=E:\Jar\IEDriverServer.exe -jar selenium-server-standalone-2.47.1.jar -role webdriver 
-hub http://localhost:4444/grid/register -port 5555 -browser browserName=ie

Chrome

java -Dwebdriver.chrome.driver=E:\Jar\chromedriver.exe -jar 
selenium-server-standalone-2.47.1.jar -role webdriver 
-hub http://localhost:4444/grid/register -port 5555 -browser browserName=chrome

Firefox
java -jar selenium-server-standalone-2.47.1.jar 
-role webdriver -hub http://localhost:4444/grid/register 
-port 5556 -browser browserName=firefox
